column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, petroRad_r, petroRadErr_r, deVRad_r, deVRadErr_r, expRad_r, expRadErr_r,psffwhm_r, z, z_person FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN Galaxy p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER by x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
